U7 chit8-pai2, chit8-e5 lang5 ti7 Au-chiu bou2 le2-pai3-tng5 keng-ke3 e5 si5, thiaN-kiN3 koaiN5-koaiN5 e5 chhu3-teng2 u7 siaN-im. I mng7: “Sim2-mih8 lang5 ti7 teng2-bin7 ah?”  Chit8-e5 siaN-im ti7 teng2-bin7 in3 kong2:“Si7 goa2”.  E7-bin7 e5 lang5 mng7: “Li2 ti7 teng2-bin7 choe3 sim2-mih8 su7 ah?” In3 kong2: “Goa2 teh chhat chhu3-teng2”. E7-bin7 e5 lang5 kong2:“Bo5 lang5 khoaN3 oe7 tioh8, chhat u7 sim2-mih8 lou7-eng7 nih8?”  Teng2-bin7 e5 lang5 in3 kong2: “Si7 ah!  Tu5 Siong7-te3 kap goa2 i2-goa7, bo5 lang5 khoaN3 oe7 tioh8.”  Siong7-te3 khoaN3 li2 oe7 tioh8.  Li2 boe7 thang ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 moa5-phian3 I e5 bak8-chiu. 
(Oah8-mia7 e5 Bi2-niu5 te7 32 ki5, 1957 ni5 1 geh8)
